JD Ive been a long time bull of JD Bought my way in in the 20s Sold in the 29s Rebought in the 30s literally the day before Trumps tweet I had hope a week after with the recovery and it lost its gain within the next two days I saw 28 as an amazing buy and almost certain it was a price algos would lock in on Faded to 2750 averaged down and still had hopes 27 I was becoming borderline delusional that there might be a miracle either via trade deal tweet positive news buy backs institutional investment etc At this point its quite clear this is NOT a buy opportunity The bottom is not clear and there sure isnt any reason why negative sentiments will suddenly shift because of a 7 drop 34 maybe 7 is a sliding avalanche Save your money or buy puts I am long on this one but definitely bearish short term We can all be blessed with a major run maybe within next month assuming this doesnt reverse back to 2324 We need either a trade deal or earnings report
